title: Egypt’s Tourism Minister reclaims position in new government
text:
Egypt’s Tourism Minister reclaims position in new government   
Sep 21, 2015 Mohamed Hisham Abbas Zaazou   
EGYPT - On September 18, the Egyptian Prime Minister Sherif Ismail formed his new government, assigning once again the Ministry of Tourism position to Mohamed Hisham Abbas Zaazou, well known for having held this position from August 2012 to March 2015.
